thread.title: Firearms debate rages as FL rally coincides with gun show

title: Firearms debate rages as FL rally coincides with gun show
text:
Firearms debate rages as FL rally coincides with gun show 5:00am GMT - 02:01 
Just days after 17 people were killed at a Florida high school, hundreds gathered Saturday in Fort Lauderdale to rally for stronger gun control laws while just 40 miles away, people attended a scheduled gun show. Colette Luke has more.
